{"tid":471692,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求AUTOCAD高手解答小弟難題","createTime":"2017-11-17T13:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T01:46:08.000Z","uid":95847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"224df5e21edee285d30092a380d609309a9b10d1","tid":471692,"uid":95847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟最近要畫DETAILING，咁畫到咁上下發現D直同橫線有問題。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/212600_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F212600_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=192e73fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明係條Vertical Line，點解會最後會有Delta X，但個Angel都係90 Degree?<br />\n唔止一條線係咁，成幅圖都係。<br />\n想有冇方法可以令Vertical Line End X 等如 Start X?<br />\n<br />\n祝高手年年升職。<br />\n<br />\n另附CAD圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1L6SKdgePLX9r9Yhix9XgGR-AJ6YRRato/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1L6SKdgePLX9r9Yhix9XgGR-AJ6YRRato%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=oC5AbjMi%2BH1TB6WHdjrt%2Fdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=af1e121f\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1L6SKdgePLX9r9Yhix9XgGR-AJ6YRRato/view?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"5dd3e651f82615548b805b1099de2984a5ccdd8a","tid":471692,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:53:13.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"70383505ff1a0e900641374c657a9b0834638d8d","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"我整咗兩張圖，唔知你明唔明<br />\n<br />\n簡單講即係將Start X 果個數Copy到End X ，咁條線就會直番。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/121124_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F121124_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG&h=f0eadc45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/121128_6bade8110601de30c47dd51084ffc663.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F121128_6bade8110601de30c47dd51084ffc663.JPG&h=db6b5840&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e5c1045bd989ad79b4cca6d7847fe6d7a02d285","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"仲有你張圖Save as 2018 version，我搞咗成朝都開唔到呀<br />\n下次你save做2013啦<br />\n<br />\n如果畫直線，記得開住F8，唔係你一手震又會歪咗啦"},{"pid":"932d55dcb83a4b51d5694b4369aa2cb1542a7bc3","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"漏咗你問果個angle係咩嚟<br />\n其實只係你畫線個起始點啫<br />\n<br />\n即係話<br />\n向上畫上去就係90度<br />\n向下就270度<br />\n咁左同右都有，你得閒自己試吓喇"},{"pid":"145390d3811f3f95884b2687c39172c4bcf696b6","tid":471692,"uid":36459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"畫線唔係用absolute coordinate/relative coordinate/length,angle?<br />\n<br />\n利申:咩都唔識的新手"},{"pid":"8ea13acd6b672a5678976ffafb7452200433f3d8","tid":471692,"uid":33216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"搭單請教各位師兄，我公司升級了win10，現在autocad有以下問題<br />\n一：dimension不能雙ckick改數字<br />\n二：j不能把線合成polyline"},{"pid":"c395537b4b55d070a68a233eec6a70f695d53d97","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畫線唔係用absolute coordinate/relative coordinate/length,angle?<br />\n<br />\n利申:咩都唔識的新手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絕對座標？相對座標？<br />\n教人果時點都要講㗎(聽聞R12前係用依2個座標畫)<br />\n但要睇情況用唔用<br />\n你畫建築野一定要有座標啦，唔跟就錯晒啦<br />\n咁簡單畫detail圖，唔需要座標，打個L，篤一下，拉出去或者打個數咪得囉"},{"pid":"332fa7757bf3612f3ba4cd753bbef5e079e58d5e","tid":471692,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"搭單問，點解我用di個陣，冇左數字即時顯示個長度，要禁空白鍵先有數字睇，點先可以較番?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a02cd2c06e10ad2b27ba80e783e9f0f5f116a70","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問，點解我用di個陣，冇左數字即時顯示個長度，要禁空白鍵先有數字睇，點先可以較番?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<br />\n你唔急㗎呵？<br />\n星期一先答你啦"},{"pid":"8530b6756910591b3e696d4a63591c97149c1936","tid":471692,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問，點解我用di個陣，冇左數字即時顯示個長度，要禁空白鍵先有數字睇，點先可以較番?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<br />\n你唔急㗎呵？<br />\n星期一先答你啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔急<br />\n但點解依家唔答得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe42588d67343806a66b5a9b8a08057f30ea615","tid":471692,"uid":95847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>漏咗你問果個angle係咩嚟<br />\n其實只係你畫線個起始點啫<br />\n<br />\n即係話<br />\n向上畫上去就係90度<br />\n向下就270度<br />\n咁左同右都有，你得閒自己試吓喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝你嘅幫忙，但嗰到有好多條線。我諗都係重新畫過佢算。<br />\n另外，唔好意思，唔記得咗save as 2013。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你......"},{"pid":"f89af608a59d1c16644c2f0c17baa6df11fcba2a","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問，點解我用di個陣，冇左數字即時顯示個長度，要禁空白鍵先有數字睇，點先可以較番?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<br />\n你唔急㗎呵？<br />\n星期一先答你啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔急<br />\n但點解依家唔答得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為冇cad喺手，我自己電腦setting都冇好似你咁嘅情況發生<br />\n<br />\n一個問題出咗嚟，可能有幾個原因<br />\n我又唔想亂答<br />\ncad個世界咁大，邊可能樣樣記得樣樣識<br />\n<br />\n你等我星期一返公司開cad試咗先答你啦"},{"pid":"b0b8f88bd10a2b9a3074fa1cab3d798ccd923bc7","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>漏咗你問果個angle係咩嚟<br />\n其實只係你畫線個起始點啫<br />\n<br />\n即係話<br />\n向上畫上去就係90度<br />\n向下就270度<br />\n咁左同右都有，你得閒自己試吓喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝你嘅幫忙，但嗰到有好多條線。我諗都係重新畫過佢算。<br />\n另外，唔好意思，唔記得咗save as 2013。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你......</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都估到你重新畫過㗎喇<br />\n不過通常我都同人講，賴過嘢就記得，下次唔會錯㗎喇"},{"pid":"fa59bb8eb933b9d2bf4e0d9a5441bef9d45d5032","tid":471692,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T18:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問，點解我用di個陣，冇左數字即時顯示個長度，要禁空白鍵先有數字睇，點先可以較番?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<br />\n你唔急㗎呵？<br />\n星期一先答你啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔急<br />\n但點解依家唔答得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為冇cad喺手，我自己電腦setting都冇好似你咁嘅情況發生<br />\n<br />\n一個問題出咗嚟，可能有幾個原因<br />\n我又唔想亂答<br />\ncad個世界咁大，邊可能樣樣記得樣樣識<br />\n<br />\n你等我星期一返公司開cad試咗先答你啦</blockquote><br />\nOK,巴打好認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f3a03eff4b8beb68b3ec5b02a8707ae1351f41","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問，點解我用di個陣，冇左數字即時顯示個長度，要禁空白鍵先有數字睇，點先可以較番?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估計你冇開dynamic input......<br />\n<br />\n我懶，只係cap咗圖，你睇吓明唔明？<br />\n<br />\n唔得再同我講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/132337_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F132337_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=559bfaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/132343_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F132343_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG&h=5ac6a9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/132347_6bade8110601de30c47dd51084ffc663.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F132347_6bade8110601de30c47dd51084ffc663.JPG&h=5c3fb1c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b151769717f38ebcd7f1b6298dce6dd711347f67","tid":471692,"uid":92854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"㩒F9(好似)可以鎖死做90度<br />\n或者你畫線時打左個線長 唔好㩒enter 㩒tab (平時換行個制)就可以入角度 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(有段時間無用AutoCAD 希望無教錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span>"},{"pid":"7eb900cbc47e053890f998342e1b9a5dabb56582","tid":471692,"uid":92854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>㩒F9(好似)可以鎖死做90度<br />\n或者你畫線時打左個線長 唔好㩒enter 㩒tab (平時換行個制)就可以入角度 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(有段時間無用AutoCAD 希望無教錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span></blockquote><br />\n無野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  原來你唔係e個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeacf0989efa9a9c2b34bb6c5e33af554dbe512d","tid":471692,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9a7fe32139d4510604b44e197347444d7a22f0","tid":471692,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:07:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"82cb963835716d6ee329cdb451340fa536dcfc74","tid":471692,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問，點解我用di個陣，冇左數字即時顯示個長度，要禁空白鍵先有數字睇，點先可以較番?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估計你冇開dynamic input......<br />\n<br />\n我懶，只係cap咗圖，你睇吓明唔明？<br />\n<br />\n唔得再同我講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/132337_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F132337_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=559bfaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/132343_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F132343_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG&h=5ac6a9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/132347_6bade8110601de30c47dd51084ffc663.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F132347_6bade8110601de30c47dd51084ffc663.JPG&h=5c3fb1c7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完巴打教學，個DI有番數字顯示喇，唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fb12589352bd7a5f4a03a46b7843225a216564","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單請教各位師兄，我公司升級了win10，現在autocad有以下問題<br />\n一：dimension不能雙ckick改數字<br />\n二：j不能把線合成polyline</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解答一<br />\n<br />\n請在command line 上打&quot;CUI&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/172637_2058009361c63ac06413494aa7ea2c6a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F172637_2058009361c63ac06413494aa7ea2c6a.JPG&h=575835e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打開紅圈果個位，如下圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/172751_b0ffa6b96977c698162bf8dda214861c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F172751_b0ffa6b96977c698162bf8dda214861c.JPG&h=96be37d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果&quot;Dimension&quot;裡面冇&quot;Textedit&quot;的話，喺Command list 搜尋&quot;textedit&quot;，就如紅圈所示，用mouse拖佢上去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/173011_d4240ffd26b8f51a14baf85d3c98ced1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F173011_d4240ffd26b8f51a14baf85d3c98ced1.JPG&h=b1b1ed5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後apply, ok, 搞掂"},{"pid":"7e436e7c075f53b357a35e7e9a6f04adebe68972","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單請教各位師兄，我公司升級了win10，現在autocad有以下問題<br />\n一：dimension不能雙ckick改數字<br />\n二：j不能把線合成polyline</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我又答漏咗<br />\n<br />\n如果Join不能將線 轉成Polyline的話<br />\n可以先試 Flatten <br />\n即係將所有線全部(手禁)平佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/174022_45ed3e5a1e47deb9c5c01fdc9389cc03.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F174022_45ed3e5a1e47deb9c5c01fdc9389cc03.JPG&h=892f3719&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e727f91f42af0d7240fc747161b786faee2dde26","tid":471692,"uid":33216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單請教各位師兄，我公司升級了win10，現在autocad有以下問題<br />\n一：dimension不能雙ckick改數字<br />\n二：j不能把線合成polyline</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解答一<br />\n<br />\n請在command line 上打&quot;CUI&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/172637_2058009361c63ac06413494aa7ea2c6a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F172637_2058009361c63ac06413494aa7ea2c6a.JPG&h=575835e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打開紅圈果個位，如下圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/172751_b0ffa6b96977c698162bf8dda214861c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F172751_b0ffa6b96977c698162bf8dda214861c.JPG&h=96be37d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果&quot;Dimension&quot;裡面冇&quot;Textedit&quot;的話，喺Command list 搜尋&quot;textedit&quot;，就如紅圈所示，用mouse拖佢上去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/173011_d4240ffd26b8f51a14baf85d3c98ced1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F173011_d4240ffd26b8f51a14baf85d3c98ced1.JPG&h=b1b1ed5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後apply, ok, 搞掂</blockquote><br />\n先謝謝，此方法無效"},{"pid":"58be6f9e007df1cfcb192badd583639c4d48deec","tid":471692,"uid":68847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單請教各位師兄，我公司升級了win10，現在autocad有以下問題<br />\n一：dimension不能雙ckick改數字<br />\n二：j不能把線合成polyline</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解答一<br />\n<br />\n請在command line 上打&quot;CUI&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/172637_2058009361c63ac06413494aa7ea2c6a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F172637_2058009361c63ac06413494aa7ea2c6a.JPG&h=575835e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打開紅圈果個位，如下圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/172751_b0ffa6b96977c698162bf8dda214861c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F172751_b0ffa6b96977c698162bf8dda214861c.JPG&h=96be37d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果&quot;Dimension&quot;裡面冇&quot;Textedit&quot;的話，喺Command list 搜尋&quot;textedit&quot;，就如紅圈所示，用mouse拖佢上去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/173011_d4240ffd26b8f51a14baf85d3c98ced1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F173011_d4240ffd26b8f51a14baf85d3c98ced1.JPG&h=b1b1ed5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後apply, ok, 搞掂</blockquote><br />\n先謝謝，此方法無效</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁離奇？<br />\n我再諗諗"}]}